---

This plugin bundles JavaScript ports of third-party stemming algorithms whose
own licenses are noted in each file under languages/ and summarized in the
README ("Licenses & credits"):
  - languages/ru.js — Snowball Russian stemmer, BSD license.
  - languages/en.js — Porter (1980) stemmer, free use.
  - languages/es.js, de.js, fr.js — Apache Lucene UniNE light stemmers,
    Apache License 2.0 (https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0).
